### Meta-Rule: Always Include Full Paths

Never say:
- âŒ "Edit the file"
- âŒ "Update the query"
- âŒ "Fix the component"

Always say:
- âœ… "Go to https://github.com/[username]/[repo]/blob/main/[full/path/to/file.tsx]"
- âœ… "Change line 105 from [old] to [new]"
- âœ… "In apps/partner/src/components/LeadsTab.tsx"

**Assume user can only click links and follow step-by-step instructions.**